MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in May rose 12.71% to NT$8,091,071,000 from NT$7,178,519,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2011           5/2010
Sales           8,091,071        7,178,519   
YOY%              12.71%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           49,250,446       52,112,751  
YOY%              -5.49% 
=================================================================
 